{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_09_01_short",
  "title": "川咲さくら (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ウエディングをテーマにしたグラビアですか？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ\n雑誌の企画で使うグラビアを撮影したいらしい",
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとの新婚生活の様子を\nいろんなシチュエーションで撮影するらしいぞ",
      "startTime": 11.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "憧れのアイドルとの結婚生活なんて\n凄く魅力的ですね！",
      "startTime": 18.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんだったら毎朝優しく起こしてくれそうかも\nほのぼのした家庭になりそうですね",
      "startTime": 25.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんだったらどうなるかなぁ\nむしろ「アイドルと結婚したい」って言ったりして",
      "startTime": 31.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子ちゃんは私がドジなことをしても\nフォローしてくれそうです！",
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、お弁当を忘れた時とか\n現場まで持って来てくれたり……",
      "startTime": 45.3666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "みんな魅力的なお嫁さんになりそうですよね～\n想像するだけでキュンキュンしちゃいます！",
      "startTime": 52.5000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのみんなの想像をしているところ悪いが\n今回はさくらが指名されているんだ",
      "startTime": 59.5000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ～、なるほど～。私が……\nえぇ！？　わ、私が指名されてるんですか！？",
      "startTime": 67.6333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}